{"tid":2497405,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇「男主外、女主內」？","createTime":"2021-04-20T13:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T13:39:00.000Z","uid":24400,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1a0298fad7126446b6d084943c82c5f9b1473985","tid":2497405,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:21:40.000Z","msg":"香港地好多人都請工人照顧小朋友<br />\n變咗部分小朋友親工人多過屋企人<br />\n好可悲<br />\n到佢哋大個都只會覺得家務係工人做就OK<br />\n覺得家務同照顧小朋友、家人係唔需要付出心機<br />\n交俾外人就得<br />\n<br />\n香港已經好細，每逢假期都要同外傭迫埋<br />\n中環仲會封幾條街比佢哋坐<br />\n<br />\n造成呢個問題係因為香港好多偽中產<br />\n無時間湊仔又要結婚生仔<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>最好加多d啦, 最撚憎見到一街外傭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老味家頭細務煮野食好難做咩<br />\nd細路仔親外傭都唔親你幾撚可悲</blockquote>罪魁禍手都係班偽中產<br />\n無時間湊仔又要生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知為乜<br />\n<br />\n全城搶外傭︱外傭身價急升　葉劉：有僱主打算開出8,000元月薪<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2496657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2496657</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n相信有部分巴絲屋企都係母親湊大/工人湊大<br />\n唔知你地點睇？<br />\n<br />\n女人結婚後應該照顧家庭 <br />\n還是要繼續返工OT、唔理家庭、請個工人打理家庭雜務？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR2MsoxraDJDar2vReRmf7vTsiY5yAx1vbHmfrcJZvUah?filename=pTvmHfv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpTvmHfv.png&h=93638a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我個人認為無論結婚同生仔都係要有經濟基礎<br />\n<br />\n兩個人各自返工咁，就好似朋友，但係一齊住咁樣"},{"pid":"e715eda0773778fbfcbe3864bc6c3726aa4890e0","tid":2497405,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T13:23:16.000Z","msg":"社會騙局"},{"pid":"c66fb39d7f2e0f626c935b481bb3518e7d6c997a","tid":2497405,"uid":24400,"like":0,"dislike":1